Definition: often tends to intensify)
Example: they said the car would break down and indeed it did; it is very cold indeed; was indeed grateful; indeed, the rain may still come; he did so do it!
Synonyms: so, in, truth, often, tends, to, intensify, they, said, the, car, would, break, down, and, it, did, is, very, cold, was, grateful, rain, may, still, come, he, do
Category: adv.all
